<!-- Title -->
<h1 class="max-w-4xl text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-5xl md:text-[56px] md:leading-[1.1]">
                        The Evolution of Automated A/B Testing in 2024
                    </h1>
<!-- Author Meta -->
<div class="mt-8 flex items-center gap-4">
<div class="h-12 w-12 overflow-hidden rounded-full border border-gray-200">
<div class="h-full w-full bg-cover bg-center" data-alt="Portrait of the author Elena Fischer" style='background-image: url("https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAyF6VncZ5uEpBL4iAxREles5-0eOChtQge6PB-eSw6SL9xS0Cp4-Vqjf_CWYOfvGE5vHMf3bHstssfc6Icpl4VqKRjXARR7K92IcgANXFNT9sHL4431zomtGXkqTL8pBVCIo90bWmRu0Nfpr8IWCbAOP13DYbav5ReZeUvZ73Mrn4PvasN6vWUAyae8Ar5eyzkM068aq_3z0cGfTBM5qeJzoRcg6LYheuRjbZgGxabbgQfqZaAef5NbnRrqmiGA_C1n1ib_OHq");'></div>
</div>
<div class="text-left">
<p class="text-base font-bold text-slate-900">Elena Fischer</p>
<p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Oct 24, 2023 • 8 min read</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Featured Image -->
<div class="mt-12 w-full">
<div class="aspect-[21/9] w-full overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-gray-100 shadow-sm">
<div class="h-full w-full bg-cover bg-center transition-transform hover:scale-105 duration-700" data-alt="Abstract visualization of data analytics and A/B testing growth" style='background-image: url("https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBJiDtPfDJzoTuWZVkkJzAQkE4pl-1dVuBCUUh9NSRl-_kNtmmAHLxk0ztNxo7LZBZZ0mBMYhA3p-lSXqyHeeFaLruAYphWSqYyhm6m15_OOYUVG-9ZesUhY6flKbQJ60aHcGuKPzDjRbk7DaarIM0G6OS6zYw70MlZvrmQUrhwp14RMoDytw8CfNUW3ASeBLxBOce7IcsDvujqpe7LbF-d9QBz_IqeDjlTnczmZfJhW0gvfKbJo7wy37rDCsqeOBe_QFeQaxnW");'></div>
</div>
<p class="mt-3 text-center text-sm text-slate-400 italic">Figure 1: Data flow visualization in modern testing frameworks.</p>
